Class SAFSAppMapService3

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.ibm.staf.service.STAFServiceInterfaceLevel30

    public class SAFSAppMapService3
extends AbstractSAFSAppMapService
implements com.ibm.staf.service.STAFServiceInterfaceLevel30
    This SAFSAppMapService3 class is an external STAF service run by the JSTAF Service Proxy. It extends AbstractSAFSAppMapService for running on STAF V3.
